                            <div data-role="collapsible"><h3>When do I apply for the business rates holiday for retail, hospitality and leisure businesses?</h3>The relief will apply to your business rates bills for the 2020 to 2021 tax year. Your local council may have to reissue your bill, but will do this as soon as possible.</div>
